  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the investigation is to determine whether Atrovastatin as anti-inflammatory
      agent can be effective in preventing from atrial fibrillation incidence in patients whom
      undergone open cardiac surgery for their heart valve repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
